{"tid":2242684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巡警見暴力場面常見背囊即截查 六男被逼後巷跪地搜身","createTime":"2020-10-14T07:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T11:00:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ca397746b34ce34d5760a8a586b0f021089133d4","tid":2242684,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"去年11月初有男大學生於葵涌被警員截查，被搜出噴漆、鎚子等物品，被控一項管有物品意圖摧毀財產罪，案件今於西九龍法院開審。當日負責巡邏的警員供稱，於餐廳內看見六名男子用膳，留意到其中一人的背包，屬於暴力示威人士常攜帶的類型，遂尾隨他們，最終六人於後巷內被截停搜身。現場片段顯示，搜身時六人被命令跪地面向牆壁。警員於盤問下承認，他未能認出被告是否被截查六人之一。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">警員1057周俊傑</span></strong>尾隨六人至無名巷後表露身份，並叫「警察！咪走！」其中一人聞言逃跑，他立即追截，男子轉頭時撞到面前的柱，最終被周截停帶回後巷。六名男子被警員命令跪地面向牆壁，逐一搜身，最終在其中一人的背包搜出涉案物品。<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問周，問他能否認出撞柱的男子就是被告，周答不能認出。周亦未能認出被告是否被截查六人之一。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201014/KB5KFD5WRVFLPN3VNL3CPSDV6Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201014%2FKB5KFD5WRVFLPN3VNL3CPSDV6Q%2F&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2qZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=c6157739\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201014%2FKB5KFD5WRVFLPN3VNL3CPSDV6Q%2F&h=5331060b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201014/KB5KFD5WRVFLPN3VNL3CPSDV6Q/</a>"},{"pid":"9542b503ee43b1450bc3fce7591774cfdce76087","tid":2242684,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c705174e8abe6a3fd4ca91de348f8d6391a3b33d","tid":2242684,"uid":354682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T07:57:22.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2